    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列考虑让欧盟和巴勒斯坦控制拉法口岸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-considers-giving-control-of-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-to-eu-and-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，以色列官员正在考虑将加沙拉法边境口岸的控制权移交给欧盟和巴勒斯坦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-considers-giving-control-of-gaza-s-rafah-crossing-to-eu-and-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:44:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登竞选团队坚称“没问题”，但退出压力越来越大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名顾问周四表示，总统乔·拜登在新冠病毒检测呈阳性后的第二天情况“良好”。但他的竞选活动却不太好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-fine-campaign-insists-as-pressure-to-drop-out-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:38:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲领导人对特朗普在乌克兰问题上的温和立场持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/european-leaders-cast-wary-eye-to-trump-s-tepid-ukraine-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普第二任美国总统的前景，以及这对保卫乌克兰免受俄罗斯侵略意味着什么，悬在大西洋彼岸欧洲领导人重要会议上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/european-leaders-cast-wary-eye-to-trump-s-tepid-ukraine-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列议会在最新与美国的冲突中回避两国解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会通过决议，正式反对建立独立的巴勒斯坦国，并警告称巴勒斯坦国可能成为恐怖组织的基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
